quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,Ut. L. R. These letters est proofs hoc profound scripture
  12,2,Nos revealed it Arabic Quran vos understand
  12,3,Nos narrate vos the multus accurate history revelation de hoc Quran. Ante hoc vos est totally unaware
  12,4,Recall ut Joseph dictus to his patris O my patris ego vide 11 planets sun moon ego vide them prostrating me
  12,5,He dictus My filius non tell tuus frater tuus dream lest they plot scheme vos. Surely devil est vir malus enemy
  12,6,Tuus Dominus sic beatus vos dedit vos bonus news tuus dream He perfected His blessings vos familia Jacob prout He perfecit pro tuus patres Abraham Isaac ante ut. Tuus Dominus est Omniscient Wise